name: Jack fruit restaurant
address: H6MW+VJ, Melinggih, Payangan, Gianyar Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: The restaurant of the superb Pramana Giri Kusuma Hôtel. Everyone is very nice et the food is good.
review 2: One hidden gem restaurant within Pramana Giri Kusuma. You will be immersed in tranquil atmosphere, great foods and amicable staff.
review 3: Very nice authentic indonesian/balinese food, delicious and well presented. The staff is very attentive.
review 4: Absolutely adored our stay in Pramana Giri Sumana (so much so we ended up returning with friends the following week), but the restaurant wasn’t quite as 5* as the rest of the resort. The food is hit and miss e.g. the half of duck had almost zero meat, the banana fritters were soggy and served with melted ice cream, the brownie was served cold etc. But then the katsu rice bowl (one day served hot, another day served luke-warm) and the rendang are amazing! All food is beautifully served. Service in the restaurant is friendly but the staff are inattentive. Almost all my meals I had to go up to the bar to ask for this or order another wine, because they don’t pay attention or check on you. They were also out of bottles of white wine when we tried to order one and there’s no shop nearby to buy.
review 5: The new restaurant just opened below Pramana Giri Kusuma. Authentic Indonesian flavour, you can also find some western food. Recommended
